**1. Clone & Integrate**:
git clone https://github.com/ringquistchase-collab/RABBIT-SOFTWARE
cd RABBIT-SOFTWARE
git checkout -b gsr-sdr-integration
# Copy gsr_sdr/ module above

**2. Build Firmware**:
west build -b chest01_nrf52840 gsr_sdr/firmware/zephyr-chest01
west flash

**3. Production Stack**:
docker-compose -f gsr_sdr/docker/neural_gateway.yml up

**4. Verify Pipeline** (14:43 CDT):
watch -n1 "grep 'φ[0-9]+.[0-9]+' /var/log/xrpl_bundles.log"